Knowledge Center
UBA Asset Finance

This is an asset product which offers credit facilities to customers for the purchase of household/consumer durables.

Feature

Qualifying assets include: Personal computers, laptops, generators, washing machines, household furniture, gas or electric cookers, electronic and electrical appliances such as cameras, video recorders, televisions.

Tenor

Up to 36 months

Eligibility

  • Employees of reputable organizations who are either customers or non-account holders
  • Partners in identified reputable audit, law and consulting firms

Benefits

  • The opportunity to acquire assets without having to save for a long period or deplete their savings
  • Considerate and convenient terms of payment
  • Competitive interest rates
  • No collateral required
